        Description copied from interface: CompactRewriter
        Rewrite sections to new level.
        Parameters:
        outputLevel - new level
        dropDelete - whether to drop the deletion, see MergeTreeCompactManager.triggerCompaction(boolean)
        sections - list of sections (section is a list of SortedRuns, and key intervals between sections do not overlap)
        Returns:
        compaction result
        Throws:
        Exception - exception
